calculations.name: Quality Score
calculations.tableau_expression: IIF([Profit Margin %]>15 AND [Heavy Loss Check ]= "Normal", IIF([Revenue Tier]="High",5,4),2)

calculation_context.Expression: IIF([Profit Margin %]>15 AND [Heavy Loss Check ]= "Normal", IIF([Revenue Tier]="High",5,4),2)

calculated_fields.Revenue Tier: IF [Net Revenue ]>1000 THEN "High Margin" ELSEIF [Profit Margin %]>10 THEN "Medium Margin" ELSE "Low Margin" END
